Sexual and Reproductive Health Rights (SRHR) Training Due
column4:
“Due” means that a visit, meeting, or training needs to be done within the current time window for completion

example: if an activity is supposed to happen between the 1st and 15th of every month, then:

From the 1st day of the month, it will show as Due till 15th of the month

column3: Sexual and Reproductive Health Rights (SRHR) Training Overdue
column4:
Overdue” means that the scheduled visit, meeting, or training was not completed within the expected period.

From the 16th day of the month onward, any activity that was not done will automatically change its status from “Due” to “Overdue.”
